    <content contentuid="h8300d99cga216g44e1g802fg4253da379ad9" version="1">气长生</content>
    <content contentuid="h8b0eb523gf117g4c2dg877ege89321c2d6c5" version="1">死亡豁免检定更容易成功。</content>
    <content contentuid="h86e86573gc282g4b56gb89ag4e8996f706a2" version="1">气养体</content>
    <content contentuid="hfe9f531bg760fg475dgab51g2a71f294c35d" version="1">每提升1级，生命值上限增加[1]。</content>
    <content contentuid="heafd6140g8985g46e0g87a8g6c9e739a8523" version="1">气化形</content>
    <content contentuid="h91389a51g2529g4c1bg8431g0b9744157463" version="1">将气息贯通到你的躯体中。在不装备任何护甲时，你可以将你的敏捷调整值额外添加到你的护甲等级上。</content>
